  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>The Cash Flow Summary report allows you to look at your transaction (payment) history, grouped by payment method, for a period of time. You can sort by the date when the transaction was added to a ticket or by the date when the ticket status was updated.</p><p>Filtering your report by tickets in Closed status allows you to look at only tickets that have been completely closed. This allows you to look at the difference between tickets that are still in open status with pending payments and tickets that have been closed with reconciled payments.</p><h3 id=\"Reports:CashFlow-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934360642/RepairQ+Accounting+Principles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934360642\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RepairQ Accounting Principles</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229524/Reports+Cash+Reconciliation\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229524\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Cash Reconciliation</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2717089793\" rel=\"nofollow\">Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541639/Close+Reconcile+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541639\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Closing a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933639827/Assign+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+to+Accept+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933639827\" data-linked-resource-version=\"22\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Assign a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) to Accept Payments</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Technical%20-%20124a6d.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Reports:CashFlow-ViewingtheCashFlowSummaryReport\">Viewing the Cash Flow Summary Report</h2><p>On the Navigation Bar, go to\u00a0<strong>Reports</strong>. On the Reports page, click on the\u00a0<strong>Accounting dropdown</strong>\u00a0along the top row of report categories. From the available list, click\u00a0<strong>Cash Flow Summary</strong>.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: If you want to specific details about your cash flow, click <strong>Cash Flow Detail</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%201.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Use the available filters to scope results based on the assigned parameters. Once you have selected your filters, click <strong>Apply Filters</strong> to run the report.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%203.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Date Range</strong> - Select a range of dates based on the date a payment was recorded on a ticket.</p></li><li><p><strong>Location</strong> - Select a specific location or run an aggregate report for multiple stores.</p></li><li><p><strong>Ticket</strong> <strong>Date</strong> - Select a range of dates based on the last status change of a ticket. This date is subject to change until the ticket is in Closed status.</p></li><li><p><strong>Status</strong> - Select whether to scope your results to all tickets, only open tickets, or only closed tickets.</p></li><li><p><strong>Billing</strong> <strong>Agent</strong> - Select to filter by a specific Billing Agent, all agents, or no agents.</p></li></ul><p /><p>If you would like to change views between the Cash Flow Summary and Cash Flow Detail Report, click the link on the upper-right side of the page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>(Optional) Click\u00a0<strong>Hide/Show Filters</strong> on the upper-right side of the page to collapse/expand the filters when viewing reports. Click\u00a0<strong>To Excel</strong>\u00a0on the upper-right side of the report page to export an Excel-friendly document. The export will include any filtered data when running the report.\u00a0</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%206.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%205.png?api=v2\"></span><hr/><h2 id=\"Reports:CashFlow-CashFlowSummaryReport\">Cash Flow Summary Report</h2><p>The Cash Flow Summary Report lists transaction totals, grouped by payment method. You can view all transactions (receipts), payouts, and net receipts. Totals for each column can be found at the bottom of the list.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%207.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Reports:CashFlow-CashFlowDetailReport\">Cash Flow Detail Report</h2><p>The Cash Flow Detail report follows the same logic as the Cash Flow Summary Report, but it displays a historical breakdown of each ticket where the payment was recorded. There are additional details that include transaction details\u2014 date/time of the transaction, which terminal recorded the transaction, and the staff member who processed the transaction. Each line also has a link to view the ticket with the corresponding transaction.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934295071/Cash%20Flow%208.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
